<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Profile Rejected - Maweed</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #d9534f;
        }
        .reason {
            background: #f8d7da;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border: 1px solid #f5c2c7;
        }
        a.button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            background: #007bff;
            color: #fff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
        a.button:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
        }
        p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Hello Dr. <%= doctorName %>,</h2>
        <p>We regret to inform you that your profile has been <strong>rejected</strong> on <b>Maweed</b>.</p>

        <div class="reason">
            <p><strong>Reason for Rejection:</strong></p>
            <p><%= rejectionReason %></p>
        </div>

        <p>If you believe this decision was made in error, or if you would like further clarification, please contact our support team.</p>

        <a href="<%= contactLink %>" class="button">Contact Support</a>

        <p>Thank you for your understanding,<br/>
        The Maweed Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
